author: Buddha
message: However many holy words you read, However many you speak, What good will they do you If you do not act on upon them?
title: Thought of the day

author: Virgil
message: They can conquer who believe they can.

author: Frank Tyger
message: Learn to listen. Opportunity could be knocking at your door very softly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Sai Baba
message: All action results from thought, so it is thoughts that matter.
title: Thought of the day
